hoven: <br />\nPiano Sonata Op.13, 57 , All Symphonies<br />\n<br />\nDvoř&aacute;k:<br />\nSymphony No.9, Cello Concerto in B minor<br />\n<br />\nRichard Strauss:<br />\nTill Eulenspiegels, Don Juan<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de684dbad435261138aa209ceccaf2caa40cc0f6","tid":373953,"uid":55511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T13:09:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>youtube search  berliner philharmonicer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你要啲咩樂曲分析<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n姐係點樣正確咁欣賞樂曲<br />\n或姐每一段樂句背後想表達既意思</blockquote><br />\n果啲可以睇programme note 上網搵唔知有冇  音樂會就有<br />\n或者係直接google 人地評價<br />\n當然呢啲只係指引 <br />\n大致睇下首野係咩黎 發生緊咩事就夠<br />\n古典時期或以前可以唔使理 直接聽<br />\n浪漫時期有 標題音樂 同 絕對音樂<br />\n標題音樂相對地有主題  絕對音樂睇曲式<br />\n但其實你可以唔使理 因為大部分好入耳 <br />\n可以直接聽<br />\n20世紀音樂 有好多唔同流派<br />\nxx主義 yyy主義  12音 請係咁二睇下wiki<br />\n<br />\n唔係首首野 都會話呢句咩意思果句咩意思<br />\n將音樂當做語言黎講（樂理上） 佢係有意思<br />\n但係哲理上 就唔一定有意思<br />\n歌劇（有歌詞類）可以有  其他就睇個人理解<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而有啲民間既音樂評論請審慎食用<br />\n例如話  莫扎特既樂曲既光明又幼稚 有童真<br />\n等等 請block"},{"pid":"3d3323b6193aa4d90e046f41377651b92af9a4ec","tid":373953,"uid":108022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T13:37:13.000Z","msg":"聽達哥清唱，巧巧天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽完就乜都好聽"},{"pid":"4bf9ffa146e156ab0d8380358661ce3f1e246d0f","tid":373953,"uid":105017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T13:24:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>youtube search  berliner philharmonicer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你要啲咩樂曲分析<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n姐係點樣正確咁欣賞樂曲<br />\n或姐每一段樂句背後想表達既意思</blockquote><br />\n果啲可以睇programme note 上網搵唔知有冇  音樂會就有<br />\n或者係直接google 人地評價<br />\n當然呢啲只係指引 <br /